## Getting started

```bash
# Requires XcodeGen (https://github.com/yonaskolb/XcodeGen):
brew install xcodegen
xcodegen generate
open <%- appName %>.xcodeproj
```

> Module packages resolve from the internal SPM repositories. Ensure your git credentials
> for those repos are configured.
